Hi - I use Rawr extensively and I just want to say what a fantastic tool it is. <br>
<br>
I am not sure if this has been asked for before, but I notice that many of the models do not have all of the available raid buffs / enchants available to them. Take Healadin for example - Powerword: Fort as a buff is not available, also enchants like Glyph of the Galdiator&nbsp;are not available either.&nbsp; Now some will say why would you have it, as it's not a Healing buff. But there are some fights that require high levels of stamina for survival - and having them all available can help make decisions regarding what to put on gear for different encounters. &nbsp; ;-)&nbsp;
